3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The study of network stability can be considered as a control problem, which could fall under the scope of systems and control. 

4. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the impact of Multipath TCP on network performance, which could potentially involve information theory concepts such as channel capacity and coding theory.
